&lt;sub&gt; - find a solution by reading the JPA/Eclipselink documentation for orphanRemoval.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;sub&gt; - set `orphanRemoval = false`, but this did break existing code/tests that rely on orphan removal. Manually deleting the orphans is not really feasible, it is too error prone.&lt;/sub&gt;

