  [2]: https://square.github.io/retrofit/
  [3]: https://www.tutorialsteacher.com/nodejs/create-nodejs-web-server
  [4]: https://developer.android.com/guide/topics/manifest/manifest-element.html
  [5]: https://developer.android.com/reference/android/content/Intent

